; LIFO cost-reduction: partial sell resolves to a LIFO-selected lot
2020-01-01 open Assets:S "LIFO"
2020-01-01 open Assets:Cash
2020-01-01 open Income:PnL
2020-02-01 * "buy low"
  Assets:S   10 X {10 USD}
  Assets:Cash
2020-03-01 * "buy high"
  Assets:S   10 X {20 USD}
  Assets:Cash
2020-04-01 * "sell 5 at market"
  Assets:S   -5 X {}
  Assets:Cash   100 USD
  Income:PnL
